    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in North Haven Upper</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">This beautiful neighborhood offers some of the most spectacular views of the surrounding landscape and makes for a perfect option for residential settlement for both young families as well as retirees.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">What with the presence of a high-profile golf course and the famous Calgary Winter Club, the North Haven Real estate a highly sought-after neighborhood in the entire city.</p>
